<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Erhu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">See also</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Huqin" title="Huqin">Huqin</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Music_of_China" title="Music of China">Music of China</a></li>
